des:
A LIVE! 24/7 NewsTalk Internet Radio Station featuring the internationally syndicated Mike Church Show, Mike Parrott's Parrott Talk, The Early Show LIVE! From London, Brother André Marie's Reconquest and our original, daily news service CRUSADE Channel News.
The CRUSADE Channel also broadcasts digitally remastered versions of the greatest radio shows ever produced including The Twilight Zone, Dragnet, CBS Mystery Theater and Suspense!
